snippet.title: Lifemates - a story of Husband & Wife | Episode 2 - Weekend | Web Series | Take A Break
snippet.description:
Prashant & Sayali decide to have a chill weekend and enjoy watching F.R.I.E.N.D.S. 

Lifemates is a story of every married couple out there. Prashant & Sayali navigate their day to day life as a couple, facing the perks and challenges of marriage, and figuring out what it takes to keep yourself committed to the bond.

- We will cover Botany, Zoology, Physics, Organic Chemistry, Inorganic Chemistry, and Physical Chemistry in One Shot

- One Shot Marathon series will start on Physics wallah - Alakh Pandey Channel on 19th April 2023

- Then, Subject wise Master MCQ Marathon series will be continue on Competition Wallah YouTube Channel on 26th April 2023

- Marathon Schedule will be provided in the community post of Competition Wallah YT Channel and Announcement section of the PW App

snippet.title: Meet Angry Prash | Episode 97
snippet.description:
YouTube Channel: https://www.youtube.com/@AngryPrashReal

Sandeep Maheshwari is a name among millions who struggled, failed and surged ahead in search of success, happiness and contentment. Just like any middle class guy, he too had a bunch of unclear dreams and a blurred vision of his goals in life. All he had was an undying learning attitude to hold on to. Rowing through ups and downs, it was time that taught him the true meaning of his life.

To know more, log on to www.sandeepmaheshwari.com

snippet.title: Home Garden Tour in Tamil | Steffi's Garden 2023 | Steffi Ulagam
snippet.description:
In this video join me in the tour of my home garden. We have couple of plants and trees that we collected over the years and some of them have started fruiting. It's a wonderful feeling to see the plants recover from the frosted winter and put on new flowers and leaves and form fruits. I try to plant as many vegetables and fruits in the space available and I find gardening very relaxing and refreshing.
If possible, please grow some plants at home and share the love of gardening!

#Urdu1 #turkishdrama #hindidubbed #urdudubbed #sencalkapimi #sen√ßalkapƒ±mƒ± #DastakMayrayDilPay #sen√ßalkapƒ±mƒ± #sencalkapimi #youknockonmydoor #handeercel #handeer√ßel #keremb√ºrsin #karembursin #melisad√∂ngel #bige√∂nal #loveisintheair #turkishdrama #hindidubbed #urdudubbed

Eda is a bright, beautiful young woman working part time with her florist Aunt. She dreams of getting her degree and moving to Italy, but her dreams are shattered when the heir to the Bolat Holding Company cancels her scholarship. 

Now only two things keep her going - her love of flowers and her hatred for Serkan Bolat. When Serkan comes to speak at Eda‚Äôs university, Eda protests strongly. A series of events then leaves these two handcuffed together for most of the day when Eda learns that Serkan really is everything she hates: arrogant, self-centred and a complete control freak. 

When the media mistakenly links the two, Serkan plans to use Eda to get his ex-girlfriend back who had left him and got engaged to another man. The unlikely pair come to an agreement. Eda will pretend to be Serkan‚Äôs fianc√©e, and he will restore her scholarship in return. The arrangement will only last for a couple of months until his ex‚Äôs wedding but pretending to be the fianc√©e of Istanbul‚Äôs most eligible bachelor turns out to be a lot harder than Eda has imagined.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3752 - 22 Apr 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3752: Babita Ki Narazgi
--------------------------------------------------------
Taarak and Jetha finally arrive at Babita's house to inform her of the truth about the car voucher. Babita lavishes them with sweets and samosas, which they devour enthusiastically. Jetha hesitates when Babita inquires about the car delivery time. Babita notices this and inquires about it. Instead of stating the truth, Jetha tells her, "Taarak adores the rosogolla," and he is too embarrassed to ask for more. Taarak informs Jetha that he should not have told her the lie while Babita goes into the kitchen to grab more sweets. Finally, Jetha admits the truth, but then something unexpected happens. Stay tuned to get further info!

James gets a krumping tutorial and the band talks about their experiences with the training system that led them to form BLACKPINK. We attempt to add to their impressive list of world records and everyone gets their Spice Girls name.

Hailing from a small village in Punjab, the Sandhu family is driven by one obsession: to leave their sarson ke khet behind & migrate to Canada aka Kaneda! snippet.title: Home Tour | Dhyan Sreenivasan | Luxury Big Budget Flat | Arpita | Parvathy Babu | Milestone Makers
snippet.description:
Home Tour | Dhyan Sreenivasan | Luxury Big Budget Flat | Arpita | Parvathy Babu | Milestone Makers

Dhyan Sreenivasan is an Indian actor, and film director who works in Malayalam films.Dhyan Sreenivasan was born on December 20, 1988 in Thalassery, Kerala, India. Dhyan Sreenivasan made his acting debut with Thira, directed by Dhyan Sreenivasan elder brother Vineeth Sreenivasan. Dhyan is the younger son of noted actor and screenwriter Sreenivasan. Dhyan Sreenivasan brother Vineeth Sreenivasan is a singer, actor and director who also works in Malayalam cinema. Dhyan married his longtime girlfriend Arpita Sebastian on 7 April 2017. He made his film debut with the Malayalam film Thira which has Shobana in main lead role. In the film, Dhyan Sreenivasan did a supporting role along with two-time National Award winning actress Shobana. His performance in the film was generally well-received by critics and the audience.

Cast: Vin Diesel, Michelle Rodriguez, Tyrese Gibson, Chris ‚ÄúLudacris‚Äù Bridges, Jason Momoa, Nathalie Emmanuel, Jordana Brewster, John Cena, Jason Statham, Sung Kang, Alan Ritchson, Daniela Melchior, Scott Eastwood, with Helen Mirren, Charlize Theron, Brie Larson and Rita Moreno

The end of the road begins. 

Fast X, the tenth film in the Fast & Furious Saga, launches the final chapters of one of cinema‚Äôs most storied and popular global franchises, now in its third decade and still going strong with the same core cast and characters as when it began.

Over many missions and against impossible odds, Dom Toretto (Vin Diesel) and his family have outsmarted, out-nerved and outdriven every foe in their path. Now, they confront the most lethal opponent they‚Äôve ever faced: A terrifying threat emerging from the shadows of the past who‚Äôs fueled by blood revenge, and who is determined to shatter this family and destroy everything‚Äîand everyone‚Äîthat Dom loves, forever.  
 
In 2011‚Äôs Fast Five, Dom and his crew took out nefarious Brazilian drug kingpin Hernan Reyes and decapitated his empire on a bridge in Rio De Janeiro. What they didn‚Äôt know was that Reyes‚Äô son, Dante (Aquaman‚Äôs Jason Momoa), witnessed it all and has spent the last 12 years masterminding a plan to make Dom pay the ultimate price. 
 
Dante‚Äôs plot will scatter Dom‚Äôs family from Los Angeles to the catacombs of Rome, from Brazil to London and from Portugal to Antarctica. New allies will be forged and old enemies will resurface. But everything changes when Dom discovers that his own 8-year-old son (Leo Abelo Perry, Black-ish) is the ultimate target of Dante‚Äôs vengeance. 
 
Directed by Louis Leterrier (Clash of the Titans, The Incredible Hulk), Fast X stars returning cast members Michelle Rodriguez, Tyrese Gibson, Chris ‚ÄúLudacris‚Äù Bridges, Nathalie Emmanuel, Jordana Brewster, Sung Kang, Jason Statham, John Cena and Scott Eastwood, with Oscar¬Æ winner Helen Mirren and Oscar¬Æ winner Charlize Theron. 
 
The film also features an extraordinary new cast including Oscar¬Æ winner Brie Larson as Tess, a rogue representative from the Agency; Alan Richtson (Reacher) as Aimes, the new head of the Agency who doesn‚Äôt hold the same fondness for Dom‚Äôs crew as his predecessor, Mr. Nobody; Daniela Melchior (The Suicide Squad) as a Brazilian street racer with a powerful tie to Dom‚Äôs past; and legendary Oscar¬Æ winner Rita Moreno as Dom and Mia‚Äôs Abuelita Toretto. 
 
Fast X is produced by Neal H. Moritz, Vin Diesel, Justin Lin, Jeff Kirschenbaum and Samantha Vincent. The executive producers are Joseph M. Caracciolo, Jr., David Cain, Chris Morgan, Amanda Lewis and Mark Bomback.

Fast X, the tenth film in the Fast & Furious Saga, launches the final chapters of one of cinema‚Äôs most storied and popular global franchises, now in its third decade and still going strong with the same core cast and characters as when it began.

Over many missions and against impossible odds, Dom Toretto (Vin Diesel) and his family have outsmarted, out-nerved and outdriven every foe in their path. Now, they confront the most lethal opponent they‚Äôve ever faced: A terrifying threat emerging from the shadows of the past who‚Äôs fueled by blood revenge, and who is determined to shatter this family and destroy everything‚Äîand everyone‚Äîthat Dom loves, forever.  
 
In 2011‚Äôs Fast Five, Dom and his crew took out nefarious Brazilian drug kingpin Hernan Reyes and decapitated his empire on a bridge in Rio De Janeiro. What they didn‚Äôt know was that Reyes‚Äô son, Dante (Aquaman‚Äôs Jason Momoa), witnessed it all and has spent the last 12 years masterminding a plan to make Dom pay the ultimate price. 
 
Dante‚Äôs plot will scatter Dom‚Äôs family from Los Angeles to the catacombs of Rome, from Brazil to London and from Portugal to Antarctica. New allies will be forged and old enemies will resurface. But everything changes when Dom discovers that his own 8-year-old son (Leo Abelo Perry, Black-ish) is the ultimate target of Dante‚Äôs vengeance. 
 
Directed by Louis Leterrier (Clash of the Titans, The Incredible Hulk), Fast X stars returning cast members Michelle Rodriguez, Tyrese Gibson, Chris ‚ÄúLudacris‚Äù Bridges, Nathalie Emmanuel, Jordana Brewster, Sung Kang, Jason Statham, John Cena and Scott Eastwood, with Oscar¬Æ winner Helen Mirren and Oscar¬Æ winner Charlize Theron. 
 
The film also features an extraordinary new cast including Oscar¬Æ winner Brie Larson as Tess, a rogue representative from the Agency; Alan Richtson (Reacher) as Aimes, the new head of the Agency who doesn‚Äôt hold the same fondness for Dom‚Äôs crew as his predecessor, Mr. Nobody; Daniela Melchior (The Suicide Squad) as a Brazilian street racer with a powerful tie to Dom‚Äôs past; and legendary Oscar¬Æ winner Rita Moreno as Dom and Mia‚Äôs Abuelita Toretto. 
 
Fast X is produced by Neal H. Moritz, Vin Diesel, Justin Lin, Jeff Kirschenbaum and Samantha Vincent. The executive producers are Joseph M. Caracciolo, Jr., David Cain, Chris Morgan, Amanda Lewis and Mark Bomback.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Episode 3751: Sachai Ki Raah
--------------------------------------------------------
Taaraka and Jetha decide to tell Babita Ji the truth after talking about the car voucher. Jetha urges Taarak to accompany him because he is too afraid to tell Babita Ji the truth. Champaklal commends Taarak for his actions in the meantime. To prepare a surprise for Iyer's arrival, Tapu Sena pays a visit to Babita Ji's house. Iyer's schedule needs to be confirmed by phone for Babita to be able to plan the surprise appropriately. Babita and Tapu Sena prepare for the surprise as Jetha and Taarak visit her home to share the depressing tale of the automobile coupon. When Jetha tells Babita the truth, what will happen? Remain tuned!

snippet.title: Starship Flight Test
snippet.description:
Starship gave us quite a show during today‚Äôs first flight test of a fully integrated Starship and Super Heavy rocket from Starbase in Texas. 
 
At 8:33 a.m. CT, Starship successfully lifted off from the orbital launch pad for the first time. The vehicle cleared the pad and beach as Starship climbed to an apogee of ~39 km over the Gulf of Mexico ‚Äì the highest of any Starship to-date. The vehicle experienced multiple engines out during the flight test, lost altitude, and began to tumble. The flight termination system was commanded on both the booster and ship. As is standard procedure, the pad and surrounding area was cleared well in advance of the test, and we expect the road and beach near the pad to remain closed until tomorrow.

With a test like this, success comes from what we learn, and we learned a tremendous amount about the vehicle and ground systems today that will help us improve on future flights of Starship.
 
Thank you to our customers, Cameron County, and the wider community for the continued support and encouragement. And congratulations to the entire SpaceX team on an exciting first flight test of Starship!

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. #kamalhaasan #maniratnam #suriya #manikandan #lokeshkanagaraj  #avcinemaawards #vikatanawards #cinemavikatan #Vikatancinemaawards  

Welcome to the prestigious Vikatan Cinema Awards Function! This annual event celebrates excellence in the world of cinema, with awards being presented to the best of the best in Tamil cinema over the past three years - 2020, 2021, and 2022. Join us as we recognize the outstanding achievements of our talented actors, actresses, directors, and technicians, who have captivated audiences with their exceptional work. The awards ceremony promises to be an unforgettable evening, filled with glamour, excitement, and emotion. Watch as the winners are announced and receive their awards from our esteemed presenters. From Best Actor and Best Actress to Best Director and Best Music Director, the competition is fierce and the talent is exceptional. So, sit back, relax, and enjoy the show as we celebrate the magic of cinema and honour the best of the best at the Vikatan Cinema Awards Function.

snippet.title: SpaceX Starship rocket blows up minutes after launch
snippet.description:
The largest and most powerful rocket ever built blasted off from Texas but blew up within minutes, in a test flight that its makers, SpaceX, hope will be the first step on a human journey to Mars. 
Subscribe to Guardian News on YouTube ‚ñ∫ http://bit.ly/guardianwiressub

After a cancelled launch earlier this week due to a pressurisation issue, the 120-metre Starship rocket system took off at 8.33am local time on Thursday. It gathered speed but then started to spin at altitude before exploding about four minutes after leaving the ground. It appeared that the two sections of the rocket system ‚Äì the booster and cruise vessel ‚Äì were unable to separate properly after takeoff, possibly causing the spacecraft to fail.
